NAG节点的出现，完美的解决了之前很多加速模型在CFG=1的情况下，完全不听话的尴尬局面。有了NAG节点的加持，加速模型的可控性变的更高了。

参数介绍：
nag_scale=简单理解为权重值（数值越大，NAG对文本嵌入的影响越显著，数值也不是越大越好，过高的数值也会导致画面失真。具体的数值要根据画面的风格来调整，例如：写实类或者动画类，特定风格等。。）不会调就默认就行了。

nag_tau=阈值筛选机制（简单理解就是筛选文本提示词的核心结构。值越大，筛选越宽松。值越低，筛选越严格。1.5-4之间）不明白默认就行

nag_alpha=混合权重（提示词介于NAG之间的过渡处理，值越低，提示词保留越完整，值越高，NAG会逐步介入参与优化提示词）我理解的应该是这个意思，不明白也没关系，默认就行。影响也不大。
色调艳丽，过曝，静态，细节模糊不清，字幕，风格，作品，画作，画面，静止，整体发灰，最差质量，低质量，JPEG压缩残留，丑陋的，残缺的，多余的手指，画得不好的手部，画得不好的脸部，畸形的，毁容的，形态畸形的肢体，手指融合，静止不动的画面，杂乱的背景，三条腿，背景人很多，倒着走

0rb4it 360 degree orbitA girl stands confidently on a thick branch. The camera makes a smooth 360-degree shot around the girl. The trajectory starts from the front of the girl, moves steadily to her side profile, and then to her back. During this encircling process, the sky naturally transitions from day to evening, and the sunset glow gradually appears. The bright and vivid leaves in the background are also gradually fully revealed.

0rb4it 360 degree orbitA figure confidently stands atop a sturdy branch, sword in hand. The camera performs a smooth 360-degree circular shot, beginning from the front view of the figure, gliding steadily past their profile, and ultimately reaching the back view. Throughout the circular movement, the colors of the sky gradually transition from bright daylight to the warm hues of dusk, with the evening glow intensifying from subtle to vibrant on the horizon. Simultaneously, as the camera angle shifts, bright and colorful leaves that were previously partially obscured become fully revealed in the background. The entire scene evokes a tranquil yet majestic atmosphere, creating a poetic sense of time passing, as the figure and the sunset-drenched forest come together in a harmonious tableau.

strength：控制参考图像对视频的影响强度

vace_start_percent与vace_end_percent：分段编码优化

tiled_vae：显存不足时（<12GB）建议开启

blocks_to_swap：通过交换数据块优化内存或渲染效率。

offload_img_emb & offload_txt_emb：多线程协调处理图像数据。（看你显卡负荷）

use_non_blocking：提升系统响应速度和并行效率。（建议开启）

vace_blocks_to_swap：压缩数据块。最大值15

steps值=步数

cfg值=提示词遵循强度

shift值=帧与帧之间连贯性。（测试建议：人物对话用5-8，快速运动场景10-15）

denoise_strength=降噪

riflex_freq_index=动态策略
0：均衡模式（默认）
1：高频细节优先
2：运动模糊优化
